ors such as databases and industry contacts analyzing annual reports and financial statements making onsite visits and meeting with top management companies that have a high percentage of shares owned by company manage perritt funds inc  perritt ultra microcap fund is an openended equity mutual fund launched and managed by perritt capital management inc it invests in public equity markets of the united states the fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it primarily invests in stocks of microcap companies with market capitalization below  million the fund employs fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach focusing on such factors such as databases and industry contacts analyzing annual reports and financial statements making onsite visits and meeting with top management companies that have a high percentage of shares owned by company management relatively low levels of longterm debt have a potential for aboveaverage growth in revenues andor earnings and possess reasonable valuations based on the ratios of pricetosales pricetoearnings and pricetobook values balance sheet and income statement companies that are in a relatively early stage of development and that are undergoing corporate restructuring initial public offerings companies believed to possess undervalued assets and unseasoned companies to create its portfolio it benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the russell microcap index and the russell  index the fund employs proprietary research to create its portfolio it was formerly known as peritt funds inc  perritt emerging opportunities fund perritt funds inc  perritt ultra microcap fund was formed on august   and is domiciled in the united states detailed description  south wacker drivesuite chicago il united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwperrittcapcomfundsperrittultramicrocapfund key executives for perritt funds inc  perritt ultra microcap fund mrs lynn e burmeister chief compliance officer and